{"questionId":"11873","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>This question will investigate methods for finding definite integrals of powers of trigonometrical functions.</p>\n<p>Let <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{I_n} = \\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{2}} {{\\text{si}}{{\\text{n}}^n}} x\\,dx{\\text{,}}\\,\\,n \\in \\mathbb{N}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>I</mi>\n      <mi>n</mi>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>si</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>n</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mi>n</mi>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">N</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{J_n} = \\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{2}} {{\\text{co}}{{\\text{s}}^n}} x\\,dx{\\text{,}}\\,\\,n \\in \\mathbb{N}.\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>J</mi>\n      <mi>n</mi>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>co</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>s</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mi>n</mi>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">N</mi>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>.</mo>\n</math></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_n} = \\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {{\\text{ta}}{{\\text{n}}^n}} x\\,dx{\\text{,}}\\,\\,n \\in \\mathbb{N}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mi>n</mi>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>ta</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>n</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mi>n</mi>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">N</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the exact values of&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{0}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{1}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{0\\,}}{\\text{ = }}\\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {1\\,dx}&nbsp; = \\left[ x \\right]_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} = \\frac{\\pi }{4}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>0</mn>\n        <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;=&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>[</mo>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>]</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>π</mi>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_{1\\,}}{\\text{ = }}\\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {{\\text{tan}}\\,dx}&nbsp; = \\left[ { - \\ln \\left| {{\\text{cos}}\\,x} \\right|} \\right]_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} =&nbsp; - {\\text{ln}}\\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }} = {\\text{ln}}\\sqrt 2 \">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n        <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      </mrow>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>&nbsp;=&nbsp;</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>tan</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n    <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>[</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>−</mo>\n        <mi>ln</mi>\n        <mo>⁡</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>|</mo>\n          <mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtext>cos</mtext>\n            </mrow>\n            <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mrow>\n          <mo>|</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>]</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <msqrt>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msqrt>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </msqrt>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11873","referenceCode":"EXM.3.AHL.TZ0.3f","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find the exact values of T 0 and T 1 .","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"f","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","AHL 5.16—Integration by substitution, parts and repeated parts"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}